      section.emphatic-text(data-bespoke-backdrop='emphatic')
        h3 To create slide sections:
        li In our example, we will add two sections: one for dogs that are available for adoption, and another for cats and other pets.

      section.emphatic-text(data-bespoke-backdrop='emphatic')
        li Select the slide that you want to begin a section.
        img(src="images/manage/manage8.jpg")

